data.description: Discover the next opportunity with this charming 3-bedroom townhouse in Haverstraw, NY. This semi-updated residence boasts a seamless blend of comfort and contemporary aesthetics, featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and 1 half bath located on the first floor. The spacious living room opens to a lovely patio, providing a perfect indoor-outdoor flow. With easy access to local shops and excellent transportation options, this townhouse offers the ideal combination of convenience and community living. Don't miss the opportunity to call this Haverstraw gem your home - schedule a viewing today to experience its welcoming charm and endless potential!
